# Runtime state (per-customer data dirs are runtime, not config).
# Voice profiles + community YAML are operator-curated and live in customers/<id>/{communities,voice_profiles,personas,playbooks,souls}/ — those stay tracked.
# Everything under customers/<id>/data/ is runtime mutable state and gets ignored.
customers/*/data/

